entry.string: This may take a moment. Thank you for your patience.
entry.translation: Kakailanganin ng kaunting panahon. Salamat sa iyong pasensya.

entry.string: You already have an installed database.
entry.translation: Ikaw ay may database na na naka-install

entry.string: If you continue, tables using the #(1)_ prefix will be overwritten.
entry.translation: Kung ikaw ay magpapatuloy, ang tables na gumagamit ng #(1)_ prefix ay mapapatungan.
